<div class="hero-section">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <h2>Welcome to AgafBot</h2>
      <p class="lead">A powerful WhatsApp automation platform with AI-powered responses</p>
      <p>AgafBot uses Groq's advanced AI to generate human-like responses based on your database. Connect WhatsApp once and start automating your messages.</p>
      <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-light mt-3">Get Started</a>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
      <i class="fas fa-robot fa-5x"></i>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="alert-container"></div>

<div class="row mb-4">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card features-card">
      <div class="card-body text-center">
        <div class="features-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
        </div>
        <h5 class="card-title">AI-Powered Responses</h5>
        <p class="card-text">Utilize Groq's advanced AI to generate human-like responses based on your database.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card features-card">
      <div class="card-body text-center">
        <div class="features-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-list"></i>
        </div>
        <h5 class="card-title">Custom Menus</h5>
        <p class="card-text">Create interactive menus and sub-menus that users can navigate through WhatsApp.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card features-card">
      <div class="card-body text-center">
        <div class="features-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-database"></i>
        </div>
        <h5 class="card-title">Local Database</h5>
        <p class="card-text">Store all your responses in a local database for quick access and complete control.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        How It Works
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <ol>
          <li>Connect your WhatsApp account by scanning the QR code (one-time setup)</li>
          <li>Add responses to the database for common questions</li>
          <li>Create menus for structured interactions</li>
          <li>The bot uses your database to respond to messages</li>
          <li>For messages without predefined responses, Groq AI generates human-like replies</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        Our YouTube Channel
      </div>
      <div class="card-body text-center">
        <a href="<%= youtubeLink %>" target="_blank" class="btn btn-danger">
          <i class="fab fa-youtube me-2"></i> Subscribe to Our Channel
        </a>
        <p class="mt-3">Check out our YouTube channel for tutorials and updates about AgafBot.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card mt-3">
      <div class="card-header">
        Support Us
      </div>
      <div class="card-body text-center">
        <a href="/donate" class="btn btn-primary">
          <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart me-2"></i> Donate
        </a>
        <p class="mt-3">Support our development efforts to make AgafBot even better.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div> 